Vote for the KGW Game of the Week ! 
KGW's Game of the Week poll for the final regular season week of the high school football season is open! 
The poll closes at 1 p.m Wednesday. 
You can vote an unlimited number of times! If you receive a "cooling off period" warning, try voting from a different IP address or wait for the warning to end. 
The winning game will be featured on Friday Night Flights and host Chunky, McKinzie & Jake from 98.7 The Bull.
